metadata.description:
Semol Birbs also known as "Burung Kecik" - is a cute loveable Birb NFT for collectors!

Semol Birb's artwork features over 100 traits and more than 10 Legendaries to collect; we believe that SemolBirb will be fun, cute, and displayable as a PFP on your socials, gamer tag, or even as a featured collection in your wallet! 

There will be 6969 Birbs and is FREE to mint. The collection will be minted on Struct, a NFT creation platform created by the creator of Kaiju Kingz, Augminted Labs! 

Whitelisted addresses will be able to claim 1 FREE Birb before the public launch! 

There's no discord at the moment and there will be no promises for roadmaps and future utilities, but what we can promise is that you'll love the birbs! 

Chirp chirp!!!
metadata.name: Semol Birbs #1
